MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

96-1809. State ex rel. Buchman v. Wayne Trace Local School Dist. Bd. of Edn.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

*1462ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
